high_descs: Turn around and go forward, turn to the left and go to the table where the computer is.
Pick up the keys that are on the table next to the computer.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the wall, turn to the left to face the small round table.
Put the keys down on the table between the two remote controls.
Turn to the left, go forward then hang a left, go to wall then turn left to face the green chair across the room.
Pick up the keys that are in the green chair.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn right and go to the wall, turn left and go to the small round table.
Put the keys on the table to the right of the rightmost remote control.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on a table.

high_descs: Turn around then turn left and face the black table to your left.
Take the keys from the black table in front of you.
Turn right then face the round table by the couch.
Place the keys on the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the green couch on your left.
Take the keys from the green couch in front of you.
Turn around and head towards the round black table in front of you.
Place the keys on the black table in front of you.
Turn to the left then move forward. Turn to the right and go to the table.
Pick up the keys from the table.
Turn to the left and walk forward. Then make a right to face the side table.
Put the keys on the side table.
Turn to the right and go forward. Make a left at the chair and walk across the room to the other green chair.
Pick up the keys from the chair.
Turn left and walk around the chair. Go forward to the side table.
Put the keys on the side table on the far left.
anns.task_desc: Move two sets of keys to a side table.
